<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>BPSU Hymn </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Calibri;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            background-color: skyblue;  /*  skyblue page background */
            color: white;  /* make text readable on dark background */
        }
        /* Centered student number in background */
        .bg-number {
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-family: "Times New Roman";
            font-size: 40px;
            color: lightgray;  /* visible on dark background */
            opacity: 0.3;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        /* Section spacing */
        .section {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        /* Page break for printing / second page */
        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
            break-before: page;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg-number">25-02897</div>
<!-- Page 2: Hymn -->
<div class="page-break section">
<h1>BPSU HYMN</h1>
<p>
Lyrics by: Bishop Socrates Villegas<br>
Music by: Maestro Ryan Cayabyab<br><br>
Dukhang pinagmulan ay di mahalaga<br>
Lahi tayo ng bayani at liping maharlika<br>
Dambana ng kagitingan at pagkakaisa<br>
Bataan, Bataan magiting na peninsula.<br><br>
Bataan Peninsula State University<br>
Tahanan ng pantas at batang bayani<br>
Punlaan ng dunong at gawang mabuti<br>
Tagumpay at pangarap<br>
Dito hinahabi!<br><br>
Matayog ang pangarap nitong pamantasan<br>
Maghandog sa bansa at sangkatauhan<br>
Kabataang matalino’t kapakipakinabang<br>
Kabataan bayani, maka-Diyos, makabayan!<br><br>
Bataan Peninsula State University<br>
Tahanan ng pantas at batang bayani<br>
Punlaan ng dunong at gawang mabuti<br>
Tagumpay at pangarap<br>
Dito hinahabi!
</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>

